"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Saudi Arabia stopped an Iranian drone attack on an oil field. The president asked Iran to choose new leaders that the White House would accept after six days of war.\",            \"english_title\": \"Saudi Arabia Stops Drone Attack\",            \"translated_version\": \"Arabia Saudita par\u00f3 un ataque de dron de Ir\u00e1n en un campo de petr\u00f3leo. El presidente pidi\u00f3 a Ir\u00e1n elegir nuevos l\u00edderes que la Casa Blanca acepte despu\u00e9s de seis d\u00edas de guerra.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Arabia Saudita para ataque de dron\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Suspected Islamist militants took over a village for two days. Troops and air strikes forced them out.\",            \"english_title\": \"Militants Take Over Village\",            \"translated_version\": \"Militantes islamistas sospechosos tomaron un pueblo por dos d\u00edas. Tropas y ataques a\u00e9reos los sacaron.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Militantes toman pueblo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A drone attack on Azerbaijan has made it difficult for airlines to deal with problems in the Gulf.\",            \"english_title\": \"Drone Attack in Azerbaijan\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un ataque de dron en Azerbaiy\u00e1n ha hecho dif\u00edcil para las aerol\u00edneas manejar problemas en el Golfo.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataque de dron en Azerbaiy\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Ukraine is using armed robots in the fight against Russian forces.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukraine Uses Armed Robots\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ucrania est\u00e1 usando robots armados en la lucha contra fuerzas rusas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ucrania usa robots armados\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Israel increased its attacks in Lebanon, causing big traffic jams as people were warned to leave a Hezbollah area.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israel Increases Attacks in Lebanon\",            \"translated_version\": \"Israel aument\u00f3 sus ataques en L\u00edbano, causando grandes atascos de tr\u00e1fico mientras la gente fue avisada de salir de un \u00e1rea de Hezbollah.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Israel aumenta ataques en L\u00edbano\"        }    ]}"